Interface DesertWell.Builder

    public static interface DesertWell.Builder
    A builder for constructing DesertWell populators.

    • Method Detail

      • chance

        DesertWell.Builder chance(int chance)
        Sets the chance of a desert well spawning. The final chance is calculated as if ( [0,chance) == 0 ). This must be greater than zero, The default is 1000.
        Parameters:
        chance - The new spawn chance
        Returns:
        This builder, for chaining

      • reset

        DesertWell.Builder reset()
        Resets this builder to the default values.
        Returns:
        This builder, for chaining

      • build

        DesertWell build()
          throws IllegalStateException
        Builds a new instance of a DesertWell populator with the settings set within the builder.
        Returns:
        A new instance of the populator
        Throws:
        IllegalStateException - If there are any settings left unset which do not have default values
